# Digital Human Resources

## Academice Groups
* [disney](https://studios.disneyresearch.com/publications/)
* [cgl.ethz](https://cgl.ethz.ch/publications/papers/papers.php) Computer Graphics Laboratory of ETHZ
* [gvv.mpi](http://gvv.mpi-inf.mpg.de/GVV_Projects.html) of Christian Theobalt 
* [tuebingen.mpg](https://ps.is.tuebingen.mpg.de/research_fields/virtual-humans)
* [Derek Bradley from Disney](http://zurich.disneyresearch.com/derekbradley/)

## Companies
* [pinscreen](https://www.pinscreen.com/) enables the rapid creation of 3D digital avatars of oneself.
* [soulmachines](https://www.soulmachines.com/) focuses on AI-driven realistic digital human avatars.
* [neon](https://www.neon.life/) of Samsung aims at artificial humans for interactive applications.
* [reblika](https://reblika.com/) is a character outsourcing studio that provides 3D character services for video games and feature films.
* [digitaldomain](https://www.digitaldomain.com/)
* [3lateral](https://www.3lateral.com/) develops innovative technologies that enable digitization of human appearance and motion, and it is a part of Epic Games Inc.

## Softwares

