#### Performance Capture
* Disney Facial Performance Capture System named [Medusa](https://studios.disneyresearch.com/medusa/) consists of a mobile rig of cameras and lights coupled with proprietary software that can reconstruct actorâ€™s faces in full motion, without using traditional motion-capture dots.

